                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col">
                    <div class="item" id="address">
                        <p>Address: 25 Barberry,Lake Forest,California - 92630 United States.</p>
                        <p>Email: &emsp&emsp support@epal.gg</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
